WEBVTT

00:00.880 --> 00:03.681
You've made me believe in you.
Really?

00:03.707 --> 00:04.866
You're engaged.

00:04.867 --> 00:07.866
Do you think I'm gonna let
some wop farm boy have her?

00:07.867 --> 00:09.786
I thought I'd have to work
to get you.

00:09.787 --> 00:12.946
I did love you.
And I loved you.

00:12.947 --> 00:14.746
I don't care what it costs.

00:14.747 --> 00:18.027
Find something that will
rid us of her forever.

00:18.027 --> 00:20.106
I used my body.

00:20.107 --> 00:22.386
They used it.

00:22.387 --> 00:25.067
How can I marry without telling him?

00:25.067 --> 00:29.346
See, he's a man.
Don't risk destroying this.

00:29.347 --> 00:30.866
What could be found?

00:30.867 --> 00:33.946
The full story of what happened
to me at Ravensbruck.

00:33.947 --> 00:37.307
To hear it from anyone else
would be the end of us.

