♪ Round yon virgin

40:16.133 --> 40:22.052
♪ Mother and child

40:22.053 --> 40:26.852
♪ Holy infant

40:26.853 --> 40:33.212
♪ So tender and mild

40:33.213 --> 40:35.852
♪ Sleep

